        "title": "feat(provider): add Vercel Sandbox delegated-run provider",
        "body": "Closes https://github.com/openclaw/crabbox/issues/299\n\n## Summary\n\n- Add the `vercel-sandbox` delegated-run provider using the official Vercel Sandbox SDK bridge.\n- Support archive sync, streamed execution, retained-session resume, status/list/stop/cleanup, snapshots, network policy, and up to 15 exposed ports.\n- Bind ownership claims to resolved project/team scope while retaining ownership-verified access to claims created before scope binding.\n- Keep OIDC and access tokens off argv, make lifecycle scope discovery read-only, and add guarded live-smoke coverage.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `env -u CRABBOX_COORDINATOR go test ./internal/providers/vercelsandbox -count=1`\n- `node --test scripts/live-vercel-sandbox-smoke.test.js` (14 passed)\n- `node --test scripts/*.test.js` (217 passed)\n- `go vet ./...`\n- `npm run format:check --prefix worker && npm run lint --prefix worker && npm run check --prefix worker && npm test --prefix worker && npm run build --prefix worker` (566 Worker tests passed)\n- `node scripts/build-docs-site.mjs`\n- `go build -trimpath -o bin/crabbox ./cmd/crabbox`\n- `env -u CRABBOX_COORDINATOR go test -race ./...` passed all provider packages; one unrelated controller timing test flaked and passed immediately in isolation.\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local --stream-engine-output` returned clean with no accepted/actionable findings.\n\n## Live Proof\n\nUsing `@vercel/sandbox@2.2.1`, `sandbox` CLI 3.2.1, and the exact local branch binary:\n\n- retained lease created in `vercel-sandbox-default-project`\n- stopped session resumed and reused\n- archive replacement and environment forwarding confirmed\n- stdout/stderr streaming observed before command completion\n- exit code 23 propagated\n- local claim removed\n- official Vercel inventory confirmed remote deletion\n- final result: `classification=live_vercel_sandbox_smoke_passed`\n- final sandbox: `crabbox-repo-1fda3e`\n",
